      "title": "AI Memory 的真正难点：为什么 Vector Store + Embedding 远远不够",
      "preview_text": "随着 AI Agent 和个性化 AI 的兴起，**AI Memory（AI 记忆系统）**逐渐成为一个热门方向。许多项目开始尝试为 AI 构建长期记忆，使模型能够记住用户信息、历史行为和长期偏好。\n然而，目前大多数 AI memory",
      "cover_media": {},
      "content": {
        "blocks": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "58m21",
            "text": "随着 AI Agent 和个性化 AI 的兴起，**AI Memory（AI 记忆系统）**逐渐成为一个热门方向。许多项目开始尝试为 AI 构建长期记忆，使模型能够记住用户信息、历史行为和长期偏好。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "f2vo",
            "text": "然而，目前大多数 AI memory 项目仍然停留在一个相对简单的架构：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 27,
                "offset": 0,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "1h63a",
            "text": "Vector Store + Embedding 检索",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "4jql",
            "text": "例如常见的实现方式：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "3p43b",
            "text": "用户对话或行为生成 embedding",
            "type": "ordered-list-item"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "a8ub2",
            "text": "embedding 被存入 vector database",
            "type": "ordered-list-item"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "ck7jf",
            "text": "新请求到来时生成 query embedding",
            "type": "ordered-list-item"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "2p5g0",
            "text": "通过 similarity search 找到 top-k 相关 memory",
            "type": "ordered-list-item"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 8,
                "offset": 10,
                "style": "Bold"
              },
              {
                "length": 23,
                "offset": 31,
                "style": "Bold"
              },
              {
                "length": 19,
                "offset": 64,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "4cmcb",
            "text": "这个架构确实能解决 “历史信息检索” 的问题，但它更像是一个 可检索日志系统（searchable log），而不是一个真正的 记忆系统（memory system）。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "2c8p9",
            "text": "真正困难的问题，其实集中在三个方面：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "2vul2",
            "text": "Memory Compaction（记忆压缩）",
            "type": "unordered-list-item"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "2pirp",
            "text": "Memory Evolution（记忆演化）",
            "type": "unordered-list-item"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "5fi3u",
            "text": "Memory Conflict Resolution（记忆冲突解决）",
            "type": "unordered-list-item"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "g4ll",
            "text": "这三个问题决定了 AI memory 能否从简单的“日志检索”进化为真正的“长期知识系统”。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "c5vfb",
            "text": "一、Memory Compaction：记忆压缩",
            "type": "header-one"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "9pr51",
            "text": "问题：记忆会无限增长",
            "type": "header-two"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "27hu4",
            "text": "如果系统只是把每一次对话都存入 vector store，那么 memory 的规模会快速膨胀。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "6eg8l",
            "text": "例如用户多次表达类似观点：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "erorq",
            "text": "I like sushi\nI love sushi\nSushi is my favorite food\nI enjoy eating sushi",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 14,
                "offset": 16,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "72mol",
            "text": "一个 naive 的系统会保存 4 条甚至更多 memory。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "707m5",
            "text": "但真正有价值的记忆其实只有一条：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 16,
                "offset": 0,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "cd696",
            "text": "User likes sushi",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "fdoi1",
            "text": "因此 memory 系统必须具备一种能力：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 19,
                "offset": 0,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "9q49f",
            "text": "将大量原始交互压缩为更高层的知识表示。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "4qu2l",
            "text": "类比数据库系统",
            "type": "header-two"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 19,
                "offset": 14,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "eroai",
            "text": "这个问题其实很像数据库中的 LSM-tree compaction。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "7dg45",
            "text": "数据库中的数据通常是：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "av5jj",
            "text": "event log → compaction → snapshot",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "bgere",
            "text": "原始日志被压缩成更高层的状态。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "5mkl3",
            "text": "AI memory 也类似：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "dq00f",
            "text": "raw interactions → memory compaction → structured knowledge",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "2o97g",
            "text": "例如：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "bjp42",
            "text": "Raw interactions：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "88etb",
            "text": "User: I moved to Seattle\nUser: The weather in Seattle is rainy\nUser: I like living here",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "eso1h",
            "text": "Compacted memory：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 21,
                "offset": 0,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "fi5o5",
            "text": "User lives in Seattle",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "72dnr",
            "text": "技术难点",
            "type": "header-two"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "btn1g",
            "text": "Memory compaction 远不只是简单的 summarization。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "79qsh",
            "text": "1 抽象层级问题",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "9qada",
            "text": "假设系统观察到：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "1rov",
            "text": "User likes sushi\nUser likes ramen\nUser likes pizza",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "4gdlc",
            "text": "系统应该生成：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "995vm",
            "text": "User likes food",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "7gifb",
            "text": "还是：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "1pce7",
            "text": "User likes Japanese food",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "4lho1",
            "text": "抽象层级如何自动决定，是一个非常困难的问题。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "674i3",
            "text": "2 什么时候进行 compaction",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "e5nc6",
            "text": "常见策略有两种：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 15,
                "offset": 0,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "d5btr",
            "text": "1 定期 compaction",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "f1tef",
            "text": "例如每积累 N 条 memory 后进行一次压缩。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 9,
                "offset": 0,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "bl3ba",
            "text": "2 基于相似度触发",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "a2kt7",
            "text": "当系统发现一组 memory 在 embedding space 中形成 cluster 时，触发 compaction。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "eh1o1",
            "text": "3 避免信息丢失",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "da8ep",
            "text": "压缩过程可能导致错误抽象。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "adg4h",
            "text": "例如：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "2hmqj",
            "text": "User likes sushi\nUser is allergic to shellfish",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "an2s2",
            "text": "如果被压缩成：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "cvvv5",
            "text": "User likes seafood",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "9u2qd",
            "text": "这显然是错误的。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "1f5ia",
            "text": "因此 memory compaction 必须非常谨慎。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "15i5v",
            "text": "二、Memory Evolution：记忆演化",
            "type": "header-one"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "4bm0q",
            "text": "人类的记忆不是静态的，而是会随着时间不断更新。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "tfpl",
            "text": "例如：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "erfhk",
            "text": "2023：User lives in New York\n2024：User moved to Seattle",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "1uu41",
            "text": "系统必须理解：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "76a8b",
            "text": "New York → 过期信息\nSeattle → 当前信息",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 11,
                "offset": 28,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "9kdci",
            "text": "但 vector store 并不具备这种能力，它只是 append-only。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "61lvk",
            "text": "Memory 的本质",
            "type": "header-two"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "6vtdn",
            "text": "Vector store 更像：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "dcn2t",
            "text": "append-only log",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "fkf7i",
            "text": "而真正的 memory 系统需要：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "7ubub",
            "text": "state machine",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 5,
                "offset": 17,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "7upe9",
            "text": "也就是说，memory 必须支持 更新和演化。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "hpoq",
            "text": "关键问题",
            "type": "header-two"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "afcsj",
            "text": "1 事实更新",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "3anaq",
            "text": "例如：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "178m4",
            "text": "User favorite language: Python",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "doe7d",
            "text": "后来用户说：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "12e3s",
            "text": "I switched to Rust.",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "9kdru",
            "text": "系统应该做的是：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 13,
                "offset": 0,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "f74pp",
            "text": "update memory",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 14,
                "offset": 7,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "85n4u",
            "text": "而不是简单地 add new memory。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "or0i",
            "text": "2 时间维度",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "ke4o",
            "text": "memory 通常需要包含：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "5ig27",
            "text": "timestamp",
            "type": "unordered-list-item"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
